# ── Rust / Cargo ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Build artifacts (the workspace uses a single target dir at the root).
/target
**/target/
# Packaged .ipk output (produced by deploy/ci/pack-ipk.sh).
/dist/
# Backups from rustfmt and friends.
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock IS committed — this workspace builds a binary/daemon, so a locked,
# reproducible dependency set is intended. Do not ignore it.

# ── Secrets / provisioned material (never commit) ───────────────────────────
# Per-store HMAC key, mTLS client identity + pinned CP server CA (provisioned at boot).
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/
**/tls/

# ── Internal design doc (kept local-only, not published) ─────────────────────
portcullis-edge-engine-TDD.md

# ── Local tooling / editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml

# ── OS cruft ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Coverage / profiling ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.profraw
*.profdata
tarpaulin-report.*
/coverage
